realtimeweb.businesssearch.main

Class RectangularLocation

  • Object
    • realtimeweb.businesssearch.main.RectangularLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Location

    public class RectangularLocation
extends Object
implements Location
    A RectangularLocation is a location specified by two latitude/longitude pairs. The first pair is in the southwest (bottom-left) and the second is in the northeast (top-right).
    Author:
    acbart

        Parameters:
        south - The latitude-component of the lower-leftmost part of the box
        west - The longitude-component of the lower-leftmost part of the box
        north - The latitude-component of the upper-rightmost part of the box
        east - The longitude-component of the upper-rightmost part of the box
